ANTHROPOLOGY: Study of human cultures and societies

Category: Science
Base skill: 20% (+5%/level, cap 98%)

Understanding how cultures and societies work: customs, social
structures, and the ways different peoples (human, D-bee, or
otherwise) organize themselves. Useful for making sense of an
unfamiliar culture before you offend someone in it.

NOTES:
  No AetherMUD command currently rolls this skill directly. It is
  available for character concept and staff-adjudicated roleplay.

SEE ALSO: skills, archaeology
